--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 2.13.0 (2020-12-31)
C: Add support for FreeBSD 12.2-RELEASE
C: Drop support for FreeBSD 12.1-RELEASE

* Version 2.12.0 (2020-10-19)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.8
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.7

* Version 2.11.0 (2020-05-19)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.7
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.6

* Version 2.10.0 (2019-11-08)
C: Add support for FreeBSD 12.1-RELEASE
C: Drop support for FreeBSD 12.0-RELEASE

* Version 2.9.0 (2019-10-17)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.6
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.5

* Version 2.8.0 (2019-05-26)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.8

* Version 2.7.0 (2019-04-27)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.5
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.4

* Version 2.6.0 (2019-01-13)
C: Add support for FreeBSD 12.0-RELEASE
C: Drop support for FreeBSD 11.2-RELEASE

* Version 2.5.0 (2018-10-20)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.4
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.3

* Version 2.4.0 (2018-07-01)
C: Add support for FreeBSD 11.2-RELEASE
C: Drop support for FreeBSD 11.1-RELEASE

* Version 2.3.0 (2018-05-22)
